in this demo we want to understand the process of Data modeling , data designing and other standard operations
   

course Enrollement Management System using MongoDB
Objective:
TO design and implement a MongoDb-based System for managing student enrollements,instructors,and courses in a university setup.
the demo will be performed using MongoDB compass (GUI) and optionally verified via mongo shell or vs code MongoDB extension
Step 1: DataBase Design - Data Modelling

        Database Name 

        Collections and Their schemas 

        CRUD operations 

        Indexing and query optimization

        Aggregation 

Step 2:  Mongo DB Atlas ( Cloud hosting)

        Free cluster (Shared)




